    "For Trojan attacks to be effective, the trigger must be rare in the normal operating environment so that it does not affect the normal effectiveness of the AI and raise the suspicions of human users 4, 54 U unsupervised learning (unsupervised learning) Type of machine learning methods based on unlabeled data 8 W watermarking (watermarking) a technique which embeds a hidden signal in a piece of text, image, or video to identify it as AI-generated.",
